Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: China earthquake
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03zjl68
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 1 Aug 1976
Massive earthquake in China. US offers of aid rebuffed by Chinese. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.